title: Size Matters, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO27
description: How do you manage the growth of your small business?  Jillian Tedesco of Fit Flavors joins Andy Frisella and Vaughn Kohler and the three of them discuss challenges entrepreneurs face as they grow more successful.
